\id 3JN - Ekajuk New Testament
\h 3 Jon
\toc1 3 Jon
\toc2 3 Jon
\mt2 3 NWER NYI
\mt1 JON
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Me nnenkul, me wo kpꞌnyono nwer nyia tv Gayus ekpondahme ejame, ye ji kpo kor-m, tib eji e kpꞌtoono etingitingi.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft 2 Jon 1\f*
\s1 Bada Gayus
\p 
\v 2 Ekpondahme ejame, n kpꞌkake ero re, ejum ajehng ajehng eja jol nob nob, wo fere jol go efel, tib eji n kpꞌkahne re, etohko eja jia nob nob.
\p 
\v 3 Atahng jo yeb-m sehng, eji abonanee bandiki ba no, ba yiimi ntianse re, a kpꞌtoono etingitingi, ano wo a kpꞌlohko toono.\f + \fr 1:3 \ft 2 Jon 4\f*
\v 4 Eyebatahng ajehng ajehng limm, ji m bahke kpe bel, sehnge jia ji m ma wuk re, abon ebame kpꞌtoono etingitingi.\f + \fr 1:4 \ft 1 Kor 4:14\f*
\p 
\v 5 Ekpondahme ejame, li nnoobo ejum sehng eji a kpꞌkake abonanee ebo go mbang anyehng anyehng, asehngesehnge ajenne.
\v 6 Bobyiimi ntianse go esamahr aneb ero bade elkoro ni a kpi no. Titi, lub kak bo ebo go bo eljen ji bo bahke tahme.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Tait 3:13\f* Lim ano go mbang nyi bahke koro Esowo.
\v 7 Tibre mbing enye nyi wahnge bo ma tahm eljen jio. Bo kpehme ko ejum ajehng ajehng goji ane baka baka ba ki nyi Esowo.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft 1 Kor 9:12,15\f*
\v 8 Wahr ba fuumu re, wahr kak elkohn ane bao ebo, eji e lꞌtob jol ane ba kpꞌtob lim eltum ka etingitingi ana bo.\f + \fr 1:8 \ft Hib 13:2\f*
\s1 Bada Diotrefes, a Demetrius
\p 
\v 9 Me n nyon nwer tv aneb ero. Diotrefes ji kpo kor-e re á jol ntubesi abo, ebten alum enyahre.
\v 10 Ngare nyi n lꞌba go, owo m bahke ba bung nsol nyi á ma lim, ana á kpꞌbungu abi alum nya ki li go etingitingi tob-r. Jol tvtv o, we nehme gbal, á kpehme vvrv abonanee, bo lꞌba. Á kpo sahde ane ba kpo seb re bo jo vvrv abonanee, fere jo kam ane bao yehke go ero.
\p 
\v 11 Ekpondahme ejame, ka jo leeme ebi! Jo leeme ji kpꞌnobo! Nne no kpo lim nnoobo, á li ka Esowo. Nne no kpo lim ebi, á ka nyehn Esowo.\f + \fr 1:11 \ft 1 Jon 3:6; Rom 2:10; 12:9\f*
\p 
\v 12 Ane kpee kpo yiimi Demetrius ntianse. Yefono etingitingi kpꞌtob yiim-e ntianse. Wahr fvfo, e kpo tob yiim-e ntianse. A kpꞌkahne re ntianse enyame li go etingitingi.\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Jon 19:35; 21:24\f*
\s1 Esꞌkohro alum
\p 
\v 13 N kpi nsol gbalee nyi kehn n jol nyono tv-a. Me nehme kor re me n ko alahb nwer, a ebti nwer nyon.
\v 14 N kpꞌbumu re, m bahk-a gulu elnyehne, e fere bung atemtem.
\p 
\v 15 Nong, elkoono jol a na. Ate eba kp-a kake nnyo. Kak ate ebahre nnyo, bo ane kpee, go nne awohng awohng.
